readme:
# atom-ide-debugger-node

NodeJS Debugger for Atom IDE.

## Usage

Run `apm install atom-ide-debugger-node` to install the Atom package.

## License

`atom-ide-debugger-node` is BSD-licensed. We also provide an additional patent grant.
